Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.82,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:41.22,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Solve the Mystery\Nof the Green Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Push. Push.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:11.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools, how dare they!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on board, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyah-nyah nyaah-nyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NYou idiots! Chase them, get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Au revoir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Chase them!\NMake sure to capture them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Wait, I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you darn smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me? I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade makes\Na bombshell announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest of the culprits\Nwill be forthcoming...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Don't mention it, Mrs. Hudson...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:17.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel guilty that someone of your\Nimportance would offer to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.\NI have lots of time on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the blue sky,\Nsurrounded by beautiful flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson,\Nyou look lovely... quite lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:36.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away\Nand ruin her flower garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! A balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:56.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kids must find it amusing to drop\Ngreen balloons into your green garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:58.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Budworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the evil gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolphin Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolphin Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what a cute letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson, have you\Never heard of "Dolphin Island"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolphin Island? No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, it's a very small island,\Nnot even visible on a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:44.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dolphin Island" sounds like a\Nname any kid could come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be the work\Nof some mischievous child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that proves to be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,if not, we may have\Na big problem on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your patience.\NIt's finally dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, thank you.\NI am so privileged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where\NMr. Holmes has gone off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give me one!\N- Can I have one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I need them for my work.\NI'll give some to you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been almost 5 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been ignoring all my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start dinner, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something\Nwrong with your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,5 hours 12 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson! Take a memo! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,12 minutes 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:27.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,31 seconds.32 seconds.\N33 seconds.34 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It took an average of 5 hours,\N15 minutes for the balloons to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the balloon that fell\Nin Mrs. Hudson's garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,flew that much time from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering today's\Npressure distribution...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,referencing wind direction and velocity\Nagainst meteorological observation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I deduced that the balloon\Ncame from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A seaplane?!\NRight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hudson must've had many contacts\Nwith air plane companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be the quickest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.\NI'll make some calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Air plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, wrongdoers are nocturnal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend all suspicious\Ncargo and check it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I am determined to\Ncapture these smugglers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work.\NExcuse us, we are in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A new case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the coach around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.\NI'll pray for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine is in excellent condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It's high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If my calculation is correct,\Nour destination should be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:25.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be Waymer Island,\Njust like the map indicates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Waymer Island\Ns... should have a lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check with the\Nperson running the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you work in the lighthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:05.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my wife and I live\Nhere alone, there's no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:09.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone visit the island,\Nor have you seen anything unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:13.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's been quiet\Nand no one's visited recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.81,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you gentlemen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be mistaken.\NWe'll look somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, hold on tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's awkward\Nmanner bothered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but then I saw the\Nballoon behind the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I turned back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So there must be\Nsomething going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"My wife and I are alone"...\NThat man was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, look up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had just gone back,\Nyou might have saved yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mister! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:33.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that\Nballoon letter was no trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they pirates? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nwe have to get untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:54.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully!\NIn regards to our plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,our target, the cargo ship,\Nwill proceed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then our decoy boat\Nwill move this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When the lighthouse goes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:08.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the cargo boat\Nruns into the reef! Ka-boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And the cargo belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way Professor, I'm not sure\Nwe should keep those two alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the job is done we'll get rid\Nof them and the lighthouse family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the decoy boat is ready, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It passed the tests perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then,\Nlet's celebrate in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:36.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not be caught\Nuntil we rescue the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to go\Nthrough the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, we'll use that tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The brat must have fallen off his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my dinner?!\NSomeone go check on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:08.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the famous "Sherlock Holmes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:13.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:17.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We located you by deducing\Nwhere your green balloon came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew you would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking so long?!\NThe Professor is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, your brat\Nand husband are captives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smugglers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they do whatever,\Nsmuggling or pirating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smugglers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, we'll do all we\Ncan to rescue your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you like chemistry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I filled the balloons with\Nhydrogen I generated in an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tools do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:23.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my dad to buy them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. I like chemistry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But he always makes a big mess\Nconducting his weird experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No chloroform or ether... hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can generate a sort of\Nknock-out gas by mixing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes,\Nlike a moth to a flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, no slip ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lighthouse keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:06.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey our orders, or you'll never\Nsee your wife or kid again, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, fill the balloons with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He's the mastermind\Nof this smuggling gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that tugboat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hurry and save my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is locked up in the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They are planning to\Nloot cargo from that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry or my husband\Nwill be an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and turn off that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?!\NIf they don't hurry and turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget your\Nwife and brat are at stake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and turn off the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, we throw\Nyour brat into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You, coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,J... Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up or I'll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the light went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The light went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We've lost\Nsight of the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous! Look sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:19:00.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's all the way over there!\NThis is bad! At this rate we'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:03.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of reefs around here!\NHard right rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, they're\Nchanging their course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out! You're\Nheaded for the reefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing\Nto my dad, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Another\Nlighthouse has appeared!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?! Hard left rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the decoy lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They came back for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat, Todd, Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:30.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew someone would find\Nmy balloon and come to rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:36.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that Waymer\NIsland was also Dolphin Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I called it that in case those\Nbad guys picked up the balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Jack, so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:59.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes, please\Nvisit us again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:05.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. You still\Ncan't catch me Lestrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:08.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty, I'm going to catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade, I'll send\Nyou a rescue ship right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward! Keep going Todd, Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:31.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NHurry! Stroke! Stroke! Stroke!
