Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.53,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden statue of an angel was\Nstolen by Professor Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:05.67,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes begins his investigation as\Nseven tiny faces appear before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.83,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes and the boys\Nstart an adventure...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:11.71,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,to recover the statue\Nfrom an abandoned boat.
